data.title: Kelly Jean Van Dyke
data.meta_description: Kelly Jean Van Dyke was an American actress and adult film performer. She was the daughter of actor Jerry Van Dyke, niece of the actor Dick Van Dyke, and first cousin once removed of Shane Van Dyke. As an actress, she was known for such television programs as My Mother the Car.
